-- EADS to Bolster Earnings With Savings, WirtschaftsWoche Reports
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 2012-02-11T12:29:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-11/eads-to-bolster-earnings-with-savings-wirtschaftswoche-reports.html
European Aeronautic, Defence & Space
Co.  plans to boost earnings before interest and tax by 350
million euros ($462 million) by the end of the year through cost
savings, WirtschaftsWoche reported.  EADS (EAD)  has aligned procedures companywide for personnel
administration, purchasing, information technology and finance,
the news magazine said, citing an interview with Chief Executive
Officer  Louis Gallois .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nicholas Comfort in Frankfurt at 
 ncomfort1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
